        <h2>Our Philosophy</h2>
        <p>Our project is based on the "sharing is caring" theory. Here, people in need can raise their requests for any
            item, and those who own such items can accept the requests to lend them free of cost. This way, people will
            be able to obtain urgently needed items within the campus.</p>
        <p>This entire process does not involve money; instead, it operates on a point-based system. To be eligible to
